@startuml Admin Activity Flow
!theme plain
title Connectify AI — Admin Activity Flow

actor Admin
participant "Admin Dashboard" as UI
participant "Admin API" as API
database "DB" as DB
participant "AI Services" as AI

== Admin Login ==
Admin -> UI: Open /admin
UI -> API: POST /admin/login
API -> DB: Validate admin user
DB --> API: Admin record
API --> UI: Admin session
UI -> UI: Show dashboard

== User Management ==
Admin -> UI: Users list
UI -> API: GET /admin/users/
API -> DB: Fetch all users
DB --> API: Users list
API --> UI: Serialized users
Admin -> UI: View/Edit/Ban user
UI -> API: PATCH/DELETE /admin/users/{id}/
API -> DB: Update/Delete user
DB --> API: Result
API --> UI: 200/204

== Content Moderation ==
Admin -> UI: Flagged posts/comments
UI -> API: GET /admin/moderation/queue/
API -> DB: Fetch flagged content
DB --> API: Flagged items
API --> UI: Queue
Admin -> UI: Review item (approve/remove)
UI -> API: POST /admin/moderation/{type}/{id}/action/
API -> DB: Update status, delete if needed
DB --> API: Result
API --> UI: Confirmation

== Video & Caption Management ==
Admin -> UI: Video list
UI -> API: GET /admin/videos/
API -> DB: Fetch videos + captions
DB --> API: Videos
API --> UI: List
Admin -> UI: View captions, re‑run AI
UI -> API: POST /admin/videos/{id}/regenerate-captions/
API -> AI: Trigger caption job
AI -> AI: Generate captions
AI -> DB: Save Caption rows
API -> UI: Job status

== System Health & Logs ==
Admin -> UI: System health page
UI -> API: GET /admin/health/
API -> DB: Check DB connections, job queues
API --> UI: Health summary
Admin -> UI: View logs
UI -> API: GET /admin/logs/
API -> DB: Query audit logs
DB --> API: Logs
API --> UI: Paginated logs

== Analytics Dashboard ==
Admin -> UI: Analytics
UI -> API: GET /admin/analytics/
API -> DB: Aggregates (users, posts, likes, comments)
DB --> API: Metrics
API --> UI: Charts/tables

@enduml
